Note:
The goal of Battleship is to destroy all the other person's ships before they destroy yours!

The board to the right is used for locating enemy ships, and the board to the left is to place your own.

[u][b][00ff00]How to play[-][/b][/u]                     

Both players need to set up their boards, placing each ship on their board.

Pick a person to go first (flip a coin)

If you go first, pick a coordinate (eg: A3), the other player must say "Hit" or "Miss", if you hit, place a red marker on the Hit board, if not, place a white one. You may need a third person to be the 'Game Master' and watch over the game

These rules are based on the standard Hasbro Battleship, but most variants such as SALVO will work just fine.

The first person to destroy all the other ships wins.
